  "title": "Payroll Lead",
  "description": "<p>This is a hands-on individual contributor role and is ideal for someone who enjoys end-to-end payroll ownership in a stable, reputable organization.<br /><br />Reporting to the HR Manager.<br />Permanent, full time role.</p><p><strong>🔹 Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- End-to-end payroll processing (experience with SAP is highly preferred)</p><p>- Income tax submission and related matters</p><p>- Claims review and validation</p><p>- Statutory and internal reporting & surveys</p><p>- Statutory submissions to CPF, IRAS, MOM, etc.</p><p>- Supporting internal and external payroll audits</p><p><strong>🔹 Why consider this role?</strong></p><p>- Permanent position with a recognized energy company;</p><p>- Clear ownership of payroll processes;</p><p>- Exposure to statutory, audit, and system enhancement work;</p><p>- Stable environment with meaningful scope and responsibility.<br /></p><p> EA license: 24S2543 | R1659662</p>",
